  <summary date="2022-09-28T15:08:42Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Domestic Violence and Stalking Victims Act of 2021

This bill extends federal firearms-related restrictions to individuals who are convicted of misdemeanor stalking offenses. The bill also broadens the scope of domestic violence offenses and court orders that trigger federal firearms-related restrictions.</summary>
